-- Microsoft shares rise 5 percent on share repurchase
-- 
-- Mon Sep 22, 2008 9:00am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/22/us-markets-stocks-microsoft-idUSN2226832220080922

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Microsoft Corp ( MSFT.O ) jumped 5.1 percent to $26.45 in trading before the opening bell on Monday, after the company raised its quarterly dividend and set a $40 billion share repurchase plan.  

 (Reporting by  Kristina Cooke ; Editing by Theodore d'Afflisio)